Global PVC Lining Fire Hose Market Insights
PVC Lining Fire Hose Market size was valued at USD 1.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.3 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.0% from 2024 to 2030.

PVC Lining Fire Hose Market Overview
The PVC Lining Fire Hose market has been growing steadily over the years due to increased awareness about fire safety and the adoption of advanced fire-fighting equipment in various sectors such as construction, oil & gas, and manufacturing. The market size in 2024 is valued at approximately USD 500 million, with an expected growth rate of 5.8% CAGR from 2024 to 2030. The demand for high-performance hoses that offer durability, flexibility, and resistance to harsh conditions has significantly increased, further propelling market growth. The rising adoption of fire safety norms and infrastructure development globally has also contributed to the market expansion.

